title: Hour 1 - College Mega-Conferences, Derek Jeter Gift Baskets
itunes:title: Hour 1 - College Mega-Conferences, Derek Jeter Gift Baskets
description:
Dan worries that college football is forming mega-conferences which will destroy traditions and rivalries in the sport. And they talk about rumors surrounding athletes, including Derek Jeter's infamous gift baskets.
